unnormalised: SpiceJet-uk baggage policy chhu jangli, pichli dafa timan wazan karith mae'n *laddoos* mae'n asli suitcase-as pyeth zyada! Mae'n Rs. 2500 zyada bhari, mae'n aass lagan mae'n chus sona smuggling karan, na ki mithai.
normalised: SpiceJet-aah baggage policy chhu ajeeb, pichli baar timan manz chhi myon laddoan tulun zyada gambheerta saa myon asli suitcase-asaa! Rupees doo hazar paanch soo zyada paye karun, me chu lagan pyowan jaseh me chu sona smuggle karun, na ki mithai.
